{"id": "1491773651547193485", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ヘロ、カーシア、ファイント、アイギスがいいと、天の声が言っていました", "timestamp": "2026-04-09T12:15:54.343000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491460187968634981", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1491773891520233553", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "全部なしだと思います。\n効率が最悪ですし、どこかしらで使ったりします。\n融災やれば結構もらえるので、そこまで急ぐものではないのかなと思います。", "timestamp": "2026-04-09T12:16:51.557000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1491733074499600455", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
